.DT
lsay
Discworld player help
lsay

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
lsay - Loud say.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
"[#lang] <string>
lsay [#lang] <string>
"[#'lang'] <string>
lsay [#'lang'] <string>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Something in between say and shout.  You might need it for subtle effect maybe.

The # can be used to speak in different specific language. 
You can use partial matching for a language, so for example
#dj will make you speak in djelian.  You may also put the language name
in quotes after the # to speak in languages which have spaces in them.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> lsay Excuse me, but I am a frog not a guppy.
You say loudly: Excuse me, but I am a frog not a guppy.
Pinkfish says loudly: Excuse me, but I am a frog not a guppy.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
emote, frimble, say, sayto, shout, remote, tell.
.EP

